sentences: Raised in South Park, Houston, Renfro gained public recognition after being signed to Capitol Records and releasing her debut album Pru in 2000.
Renfro's debut album Pru was released the record on November 7, 2000.
Pru reached a peak position of number 176 on the Billboard 200, spending two weeks on the chart, and peaked on Billboard's R&B Albums at number 38, leaving the chart after thirty-two weeks.
